TITLE: Building and Running Loki from Source (Bash)
DESCRIPTION: Instructions for building Loki from source code and running it in a single-host, no-dependencies mode. Requires an up-to-date version of Go.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/loki/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
