TITLE: Querying Log Statistics
DESCRIPTION: Command to retrieve statistics about queried log data including bytes, chunks, streams, and entries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/loki/blob/main/docs/sources/query/logcli/logcli-tutorial.md#2025-04-19_snippet_9

