TITLE: Calculating Cost of Discarded Events in LogQL
DESCRIPTION: This LogQL query calculates the cost of discarded events per user, organization, and namespace. It uses group_left to include labels from the right-hand side in the result.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/loki/blob/main/docs/sources/query/_index.md#2025-04-19_snippet_14

