TITLE: Decoding an S2 Compressed Stream in Go
DESCRIPTION: This function demonstrates how to decompress data from an S2 compressed stream. It creates a new S2 reader and copies all data from the decoder to the destination writer. The decoder can handle both S2 and Snappy compressed content.
