TITLE: Configuring OpenTelemetry Context Propagation in HTTP-based Go Clients
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to pass options to OpenTelemetry trace context propagation in HTTP-based clients. It shows configuration of an HTTP transport with custom filtering options for OpenTelemetry.
