TITLE: Defining RulesSpec and LokiStack API Extensions in Go
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the Go structs necessary for extending the LokiStack API to support the Ruler component. It includes RulesSpec for enabling/disabling the ruler and selecting rules, as well as extensions to LokiStackSpec, LokiTemplateSpec, and LokiStackComponentStatus.
