TITLE: Starting Promtail Service via Bash Commands
DESCRIPTION: A set of Bash commands to deploy and start the Promtail service. It includes downloading the Promtail binary, creating necessary directories, setting up the configuration files, and enabling the systemd service.
SOURCE: https://github.com/grafana/loki/blob/main/operator/hack/boilerplate.go.txt#2025-04-19_snippet_2

